DRAFT — pending operator review. Not yet ratified. (2026-07-11)

This repository's `package.json` declares its license as the SPDX expression
`Zlib AND LicenseRef-Tinyland-Proprietary`, but no `LICENSE` file existed in
the repository prior to this draft, and no text for
`LicenseRef-Tinyland-Proprietary` exists anywhere in this repo or elsewhere
in the org as of this writing. This file is a starting point, not a
ratified license grant: the Zlib portion below is the standard, public,
unmodified license text (safe to vendor verbatim), and the proprietary
portion is an explicit placeholder that must be filled in and reviewed by
the operator before this file can be treated as authoritative.

